<plot>Documentary profiling Johnny Briggs, the actor best known for playing 'Mike Baldwin' in the British soap opera 'Coronation Street' since 1976. The programme goes behind the scenes of the popular serial and reveals the man behind the character. His co-stars and family pay tribute to him and clips are shown from his early movie career.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?369508</url></doc>
